    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/c598f3-79/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=612368322326954795&sectionId=612368322377548587)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9Bxa_cYv0_text","label":"gg9Bxa_cYv0_text","default":"People Notice the Difference"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwgn5YyW7s_text","label":"ggwgn5YyW7s_text","default":"<p>I got relief from tension in my jaw, neck, shoulders and back from day one. The mouth guard or plackers make me aware of jaw clenching instantly, and I stop doing it. I knew my jaw was tight before, but I thought it was a tension headache, not the cause of all the tension.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeECchcoBQ_text","label":"ggeECchcoBQ_text","default":"<p>- Stella</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_bkok-kRn_text","label":"gg_bkok-kRn_text","default":"<p>I cannot stress enough how much has changed: strength, balance, sleep, focus… and the list goes on. I finally did my first pull-ups after years of training, not from more effort, but from better connection. I effortlessly move, stretch, lift. This process is not linear. More like a cycle.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVB5y_QJGW_text","label":"ggVB5y_QJGW_text","default":"<p>- Barbora</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggyaX9ZvT3T_text","label":"ggyaX9ZvT3T_text","default":"<p>As soon as I put the Reviv into my mouth, my head raises up and my posture improves. It improves my posture, allowing me to relax my upper body, decreasing fatigue. Lifting my head up also lifts my chest, allowing proper breathing. All positives, and it’s immediate.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcMs92oiZz_text","label":"ggcMs92oiZz_text","default":"<p>- George</p>"}],
    "blocks": [{"type": "@app"}],
    "locales": {}
